f says Ukraine invasion plan 'malicious' U.S. propaganda |url=https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/russia-spy-chief-says-ukraine-invasion-plan-malicious-us-propaganda-2021-11-27/ |work=Reuters |date=2021-11-27 |accessdate=2022-02-25 |archive-date=2021-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211222034441/https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/russia-spy-chief-says-ukraine-invasion-plan-malicious-us-propaganda-2021-11-27/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=West voices its concern over Russia's military build-up on Ukrainian border ahead of Biden call with Putin |url=https://news.sky.com/story/west-voices-its-concern-over-russias-military-build-up-on-ukrainian-border-ahead-of-biden-call-with-putin-12488742 |work=Sky News |date=2021-12-07 |accessdate=2022-02-25 |archive-date=2022-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124114246/https://news.sky.com/story/west-voices-its-concern-over-russias-military-build-up-on-ukrainian-border-ahead-of-biden-call-with-putin-12488742 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Russia denies looking for pretext to invade Ukraine |url=https://apnews.com/article/russia-officials-ukraine-invasion-f58cbbd7eca51cccf74ebd4be68484e8 |work=Associated Press |date=2022-01-17 |accessdate=2022-02-25 |archive-date=2022-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122131745/https://apnews.com/article/russia-officials-ukraine-invasion-f58cbbd7eca51cccf74ebd4be68484e8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

